# direnv configuration for automatic shell loading
# Install direnv and run: direnv allow
#
# This will automatically load the Vulkan RADV dev shell when you cd into this directory.
# 
# To use a different backend, change the devShell below:
#   - .#vulkan-radv   (default, most stable)
#   - .#vulkan        (alias for vulkan-radv)
#   - .#rocm          (AMD's GPU compute stack)

use flake .#vulkan-radv
